OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight
OL,6,Fshowers possible for Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway this evening, but largely dry
OL,8,Fwith late sunny spells in the east.
OL,9,FClearing skies overnight will then
OL,10,Fbring a touch of frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA touch of frost first
OL,13,Fthing in the morning for some. It will
OL,14,Fthen be a dry and bright day with a
OL,15,Ffew rather hazy sunny spells between
OL,16,Fpatchy cloud.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,19,Fgood deal of cloud around during this
OL,20,Fperiod with showers, but some brighter
OL,21,Fperiods. Rather breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
